00:17:15,009 --> 00:17:20,679
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我该怎么做…才能保住这颗左眼啊</font>

296
00:17:23,939 --> 00:17:29,299
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我做不到…在没有爸爸妈妈的黑暗岁月里</font>

297
00:17:29,359 --> 00:17:33,109
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">没有这颗左眼 我是活不下去的</font>

298
00:17:34,569 --> 00:17:35,759
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">「并非如此」</font>

299
00:17:36,259 --> 00:17:38,249
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">如此安慰她是很简单的事情</font>

300
00:17:38,629 --> 00:17:41,309
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">但光是这样 无法拯救斋川</font>

301
00:17:42,059 --> 00:17:44,659
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">她在一片黑暗之中 拼命地当着偶像</font>

302
00:17:44,749 --> 00:17:49,119
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">现在更是独自拿着手枪在战斗</font>

303
00:17:49,639 --> 00:17:52,659
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">那到底什么才能拯救她？</font>

304
00:17:53,109 --> 00:17:56,919
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">她现在最想要的是…</font>

305
00:17:57,149 --> 00:18:01,609
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我们本来计划好了 在这个案子结束后 就去海边玩</font>

306
00:18:03,519 --> 00:18:08,289
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">然后 如果斋川愿意的话 就带你一起去</font>

307
00:18:10,259 --> 00:18:16,029
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">也就是说 你愿不愿意当我们的朋友？</font>

308
00:18:17,349 --> 00:18:23,099
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">为什么？我可是想杀了你们啊</font>

309
00:18:23,749 --> 00:18:27,919
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">没事 我们可不会轻易地就死了</font>

310
00:18:28,249 --> 00:18:32,709
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">不行的 我没有那种资格</font>

311
00:18:33,309 --> 00:18:35,269
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">这应该由我来决定</font>

312
00:18:36,009 --> 00:18:37,829
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">但是…但是…</font>

313
00:18:38,489 --> 00:18:41,189
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我想和你当朋友</font>

314
00:18:43,849 --> 00:18:46,579
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">愿意听我这个任性的请求吗</font>

315
00:18:50,289 --> 00:18:54,659
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你这人真怪 夏凪 这也太…</font>

316
00:18:55,119 --> 00:19:02,049
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">是吗？但是我最近觉得 和怪人当朋友肯定会很开心的</font>

317
00:19:02,259 --> 00:19:08,299
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">就算…就算我们成了朋友 也解决不了问题啊</font>

318
00:19:08,689 --> 00:19:12,149
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">反而会给你们添更多的麻烦</font>

319
00:19:12,509 --> 00:19:13,919
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我觉得不会</font>

320
00:19:17,969 --> 00:19:23,709
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">斋川 如果你想说你已经被他们盯上了 那我也是一样</font>

321
00:19:24,219 --> 00:19:27,889
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">别觉得会添麻烦 大家都是同病相怜的目标</font>

322
00:19:28,239 --> 00:19:31,349
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">干脆结盟还更好一点</font>

323
00:19:32,079 --> 00:19:34,829
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你愿意帮我吗？</font>

324
00:19:35,479 --> 00:19:37,359
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">嗯 会帮你</font>

325
00:19:38,079 --> 00:19:39,309
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">所以 斋川</font>

326
00:19:40,439 --> 00:19:42,399
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我希望你能成为我们的同伴</font>

327
00:19:49,799 --> 00:19:52,019
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">好的 我很乐意</font>

328
00:19:54,539 --> 00:19:59,759
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">每次醒来 你都在我身边</font>

329
00:19:59,909 --> 00:20:05,059
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">给我一个全新的早晨</font>

330
00:20:05,059 --> 00:20:10,439
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">那心跳是如此温柔</font>

331
00:20:10,439 --> 00:20:15,409
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">却又悲伤得催人泪下</font>

332
00:20:15,759 --> 00:20:21,039
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">在大声叫喊着 想要见到某人</font>

333
00:20:21,109 --> 00:20:26,439
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">却又不知道名字和长相</font>

334
00:20:26,439 --> 00:20:31,759
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">但我真的听到了那声音</font>

335
00:20:31,759 --> 00:20:36,329
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">只能漫无目的地去探寻</font>

336
00:20:36,719 --> 00:20:42,009
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">虽然可能只会徒增烦恼</font>

337
00:20:42,059 --> 00:20:50,099
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">但这不是为了别人而是为了自己</font>

338
00:20:51,899 --> 00:20:57,199
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">胸膛中的声音 那声呐喊 指引着我前进</font>

339
00:20:57,199 --> 00:21:02,519
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">将零落的心意捡起 送到它想去的地方吧</font>

340
00:21:02,519 --> 00:21:07,769
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">因为是你告诉我生命的意义</font>

341
00:21:07,769 --> 00:21:15,789
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">让我觉得 这个世界也许还没那么坏</font>

342
00:21:26,879 --> 00:21:28,839
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">(娱乐新闻 拯救偶像斋川唯 立下大功的高中生)</font>

343
00:21:39,349 --> 00:21:40,099
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">女士</font>

344
00:21:44,049 --> 00:21:44,979
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">女士！</font>

345
00:21:45,119 --> 00:21:47,719
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">为什么要我和这种男人组成搭档啊！</font>

346
00:21:48,049 --> 00:21:52,429
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">与其和君冢组合 我宁愿现在就跳海</font>

347
00:21:52,789 --> 00:21:55,089
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我可以帮你保管贵重物品</font>

348
00:21:56,459 --> 00:21:59,269
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我才是女士的头号弟子啊！</font>

349
00:21:59,729 --> 00:22:02,289
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">这是临时性的策略 夏洛</font>

350
00:22:03,319 --> 00:22:03,999
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">过来</font>

351
00:22:04,989 --> 00:22:06,299
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">女士！</font>

352
00:22:07,239 --> 00:22:08,499
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">乖 乖</font>

353
00:22:13,249 --> 00:22:14,959
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">不 我一点都不羡慕啊</font>

354
00:22:15,599 --> 00:22:21,559
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">如果你们关系能好一点 我也能省点心</font>

355
00:22:23,339 --> 00:22:27,539
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我还没答应要和君冢一起行动呢！</font>

356
00:22:27,879 --> 00:22:31,039
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">听好了 你们两个都不完美</font>

357
00:22:31,619 --> 00:22:34,039
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">比如说助手 虽然脑袋聪明</font>

358
00:22:34,229 --> 00:22:39,129
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">但很遗憾的是体力连跳蚤都不如 完全不适合战斗</font>

359
00:22:40,099 --> 00:22:41,559
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">是吗</font>

360
00:22:43,109 --> 00:22:49,069
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">而夏洛虽然战斗能力很强 但脑袋却非常笨</font>

361
00:22:49,299 --> 00:22:50,349
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">什么！</font>

362
00:22:53,099 --> 00:23:00,359
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">所以 我希望这次你们能互相补足缺点 完成任务</font>

363
00:23:00,719 --> 00:23:03,249
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">但是 这样就要丢下女士你一个人…</font>

364
00:23:03,919 --> 00:23:08,289
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">可别看不起我 我有着十倍于夏洛的武力</font>

365
00:23:08,779 --> 00:23:13,839
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">以及百倍于助手的头脑 不需要你们担心</font>

366
00:23:14,859 --> 00:23:17,879
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你对我的评价有问题吧</font>

367
00:23:21,009 --> 00:23:21,489
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">听好了</font>

368
00:23:22,439 --> 00:23:26,569
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">总之 你们两个要好好相处哦</font>

369
00:23:27,119 --> 00:23:28,999
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">今后也是 永远如此</font>

370
00:23:30,439 --> 00:23:31,729
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">而在那一天</font>

371
00:23:32,709 --> 00:23:34,259
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">大侦探死了</font>

372
00:23:35,929 --> 00:23:40,929
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">(第5集 那是为了一年后的未来)</font>

